'''''Terminator''''' was an [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate]] in the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The ''Terminator'' was dispatched to attack the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Mon Calamari Star Cruiser/Legends|Mon Calamari Star Cruiser]] ''[[Cathleen]]'' while it was recovering battle-weary [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] returning from a successful attack on [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] shipping in [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]]. The ''Terminator'' launched [[TIE/sa tactical bomber/Legends|TIE/sa bombers]] to destroy the vulnerable Rebel ships, but two [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|T-65 X-wing starfighters]] and two [[RZ-1 A-wing interceptor/Legends|RZ-1 A-wing interceptors]] from [[Red Squadron (Rebel Alliance)/Legends|Red Squadron]] held off the Imperial fighters while the ''Cathleen'' recovered the other Rebel ships and escaped.

